* {{enPR|klĭng'ŏn}}, {{IPA|/ˈklɪŋɒn/}}, {{SAMPA|/"klINQn/}}
* {{IPA|/ˈklɪŋɑn/}}, {{SAMPA|/"klINAn/}}<!-- cot-caught merger or just US-style IPA? -->

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{countable}} Member of an alien warrior race in the Star Trek universe, depicted as having distinctive forehead ridges and a culture based on strict observance of honour, loyalty, and combat.

